.08); flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden; }\r\n.review-right { flex: 1; padding: 16px; overflow-y: auto; }\r\n.empty-hint { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }\r\n</style>\r\n"
